Name: AA Widgets

Caption.String: This form shows all data entry widgets. They are defined in src/widgets.cpp or src/uiobjects.cpp.

Callbacks: This form is for testing widgets.
* Wiget Label property determines table column label
* Variable Index Labels property should be same as
widget label followed by comma and number indicating
mode to work properly in inputs browser. For example:
msgbox('initial value of x is = ' + x );
msgbox('incremented value of x is ' + x );
